Package io.covrsecurity.onyonservice

Class OnyonConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.dropwizard.Configuration
      • io.covrsecurity.onyonservice.OnyonConfiguration
  • public class OnyonConfiguration
extends io.dropwizard.Configuration
    Holds the configuration for the Onyon Service. This is read from the config yml-file and part of Dropwizard.
